?1 What is server :
	A server is a computer that handles a specific 
	task or provides data to other computers over a
	network

?2 What is the role of the domain name:
	A domain name is a unique name that identifies a
	website or an online service
	Domain names make it easier for people to remember
	and access websites without typing long numerical 
	addresses

?3 What type of DNS record `www` is in `www.foobar.com`:
	The www part of a domain name is usually an A record
	that points to the IP address of a web server

?4 What is the role of the web server:
	A web server is a computer that stores, processes,
	and delivers website files to web browsers

?5 What is the role of the application server:
	An application server is a server that hosts 
	applications or software that deliver a business 
	function through a communication protocol

?6 What is the role of the database:
	* Transforming raw data into useful information
	* Distributing data and information to the right 
	  people at the right time
	* Preserving and monitoring data usage for adequate 
	  periods of time
	* Controlling data duplication and use, both internally 
	  and externally

?7 What is the server using to communicate with the computer of the user requesting -
   the website
	HTTP(HyperTextTransferProtocol) protocol
